build.md
     1вЖТ# The build command
     3вЖТThe build command is used to render your book:
     4вЖТ
     5вЖТ```bash
     6вЖТmdbook build
     7вЖТ```
     8вЖТ
     9вЖТIt will try to parse your `SUMMARY.md` file to understand the structure of your
    10вЖТbook and fetch the corresponding files. Note that this will also create files
    11вЖТmentioned in `SUMMARY.md` which are not yet present.
    12вЖТ
    13вЖТThe rendered output will maintain the same directory structure as the source for
    14вЖТconvenience. Large books will therefore remain structured when rendered.
    15вЖТ
    16вЖТ#### Specify a directory вА¶
    25вЖТ#### `--open` вА¶
    30вЖТ#### `--dest-dir` вА¶

